itting, screening, grease removal and nutrient removal is to be constructed. This project involves civil, E&M works and all other ancillary building services, architectural, landscape and establishment works; construction of a submarine outfall of approximately 500m long at Yung Shue Wan of which a minimum 400m of submarine outfall from the coastline shall be constructed by Horizontal Directional Drilling.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The major works of this project also include construction of a sewage treatment works at Sok Kwu Wan on Lamma Island, involving civil, E&M works and all other ancillary building services, architectural, landscape and establishment works and approximately 600m rising main from Sok Kwu Wan Sewage Treatment Works to the outfall chamber; construction of a submarine outfall of approximately 750m long at Sok Kwu Wan of which a minimum 650m of submarine outfall from the coastline shall be constructed by Horizontal Directional Drilling.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"This project is the first time Horizontal Directional Drilling has been adopted in Hong Kong. It offers significant environmental advantages over traditional cut and cover pipeline/utility installations.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]'),(110,'rplfadyb9kfsq88kqt6vrv6l','Management Contract for the Residential Development at No.420-422 Prince Edward Road West','2025-05-29 11:26:33.259000','2025-06-27 08:52:47.688000','2025-06-27 08:52:47.751000',8,3,'en','Management Contract for the Residential Development at No.420-422 Prince Edward Road West','Wise City Investment Limited','29 December 2015 - 14 May 2018','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The property is a residential development located at No.420-420 Prince Edward Road West, Kowloon City, Kowloon, Hong Kong. Build King enters into Management Contracts with the client and provides Management Services covering the co